				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Line 0 is used to initialize the sprite engine. Before HBlank the sprites for line 1 are determined, and during HBlank their tiles are loaded from VRAM. Neither sprites nor backgrounds are displayed in line 0.<br /><br />Afaik when a background has a vertical scroll value of 0, its first line would've been in screen line 0, but is skipped because line 0 is not displayed. I'd guess the same goes for sprites.</div>

